===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} ''[[securite]]'', from {{etyl|fro}} (French: ''[[sécurité]]''), from {{etyl|la}} ''[[securitas]]'', from {{etyl|la}} ''[[securus]]'' "[[safe]], [[secure]]".

